'''Edwin Mahinda''' , umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Kenya]] wacyuye igihe. <ref>https://www.fernsehserien.de/edwin-mahinda/filmografie</ref> <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/38884.html</ref> Gutangira umwuga we wa sinema nkumuhanzi wumwana, Mahinda azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''The Kitchen Toto'', ''White Mischief'' and ''The Lion of Africa''. <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2ba54853d1</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/edwin-mahinda</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1987, Mahinda yagaragaye bwa mbere muri sinema hamwe na firime yo mu Bwongereza yitwa ''The Kitchen Toto'' . <ref>https://www.evasguide.com/east-africa/movies/kitchen-toto/</ref> Yakinnye cyane 'Mwangi' muri iyi filime, aho yaje gutsindira igihembo cya Festival ya Paris igihembo cyumukinnyi mwiza. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20090115141601/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/256286</ref> Intsinzi ya firime, yahise atoranywa muri firime ya ''White Mischief'' yo mu 1987 kubera uruhare ruto rwa 'Umuhungu Wategereje kuri Wake'. Ariko, mu 1988, yongeye kugira uruhare mu gushyigikira 'Umuvandimwe wa Joko' muri filime y'Abanyamerika ''The Lion of Africa'' . Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 28 Kamena 1987, kuri HBO . <ref>http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1988-02-14/entertainment/8803300319_1_lion-brian-dennehy-theater-screen</ref>

Mu 1989, Mahinda yagaragaye bwa nyuma muri firime. Yakinnye nka 'Moja' muri ''Piramiddo nta kanata ni: Intare yera densetsu'' .

